snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Year 1 Character Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Four fighters join the Street Fighter 6 roster in our first year after launch! Rashid returns in Summer 2023. A.K.I. struts into the roster in Autumn 2023. Ed strikes back in Winter 2024. The legend, the beast, the transcendent Akuma will rage into Street Fighter 6 in Spring 2024! 

All four of these characters are also incorporated into World Tour where you can learn their Special Moves and increase your bond. Year 1 Characters are also included in the Deluxe and Ultimate Editions of Street Fighter 6.

Pre-Order Now - https://streetfighter.com/6/en-us/

#StreetFighter6 #Capcom #Rashid #AKI #Ed #Akuma
